## Test Structure & Export Checklist for New Domains

Based on my thorough exploration of the codebase, here's what needs to be updated when adding new domains:

---

### **1. Folder Structure Overview**

**Complete domains (airlineMiles, parameter, permission, extract):**

```
src/services/
├── api/
│   ├── airlineMiles.api.ts
│   ├── parameter.api.ts
│   ├── permission.api.ts
